ingredient: 5 boneless skinless chicken thighs (about 1/3 lb. each)
1 tsp salt (to salt water for boiling)
1/2 lb. ground pork, chicken or turkey
12 oz. seasoning mix (frozen chopped onion, bell pepper, celery)
2 tsp Active Dry or instant yeast
2 cups all-purpose flour (plus some for dusting)
1 Tbsp finely chopped fresh parsley, loosely packed
